Detailed Description

cvmx_pko_mem_debug12

Notes: Internal per-engine x4 state intended for debug use only - pko.out.ctl.cmnd[63:0] This CSR is a memory of 40 entries, and thus, the PKO_REG_READ_IDX CSR must be written before any CSR read operations to this address can be performed.
